HEADWORD: Texas
<hw>Tex"as</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A structure on the
hurricane deck of a steamer, containing the pilot house, officers'
cabins, etc.</def> <mark>[Western U. S.]</mark>
